<p><i><b>The Unbearable Lightness of Being</b></i> (<a href="/wiki/Czech_language" title="Czech language">Czech</a>: <span lang="cs" xml:lang="cs"><i>Nesnesitelná lehkost bytí</i></span>) is a <a href="/wiki/Novel" title="Novel">novel</a> written by <a href="/wiki/Milan_Kundera" title="Milan Kundera">Milan Kundera</a> in 1982, first published in <a href="/wiki/1984_in_literature" title="1984 in literature">1984</a> in France.</p>
